snippet.title: The Blind Architect Revolutionizing Design | Chris Downey & Amber Schleuning | Wondros Podcast Ep115
snippet.description:
Jesse and Priscilla talk to archetect Chris Downey, who lost his sight and saw new ways to design spaces that enrich everyone's lives.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

About Series:
Wondros Podcast is moderated by Jesse Dylan, Founder of Wondros and Priscilla Cohen, Chief Creative Officer at Wondros. The show covers interesting conversations with fascinating people. 

About Wondros:
